</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Last January, GameStop Corp.=E2=80=99s=
 stock went up 1,625% on huge volume with lots of volatility for <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26731524.281600/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDEtMjUvdGhlLWdhbWUtbmV=
2ZXItc3RvcHM_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDIxNjIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG=
1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIwMjE2JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0d=
WZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB14a0aee0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"=
itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> no obvious reason</a>. It w=
as the leading story in national news for days, and by mid-February there w=
ere <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26731524.28160=
0/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhld3JhcC5jb20vbWFrZS1pdC1nYW1lc3RvcC1hbGwtdGhlLWNvbXBld=
GluZy1maWxtLWFuZC10di1wcm9qZWN0cy1pbi10aGUtd29ya3MtYWJvdXQtdGhlLXdhbGxzdHJl=
